![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f8c37627-eeed-4f2e-b681-bfdd487c4dfe/E315.jpg)

What If is back with a brand-new season, and with brand-new scenarios taking place all over Marvel's multiverse. Some stories are bleak, others light-hearted and some are just overall epic. We get a return of certain characters, albeit with slightly confusing motivations but the energy is still palpable. Join us as we go episode by episode and recap and review the events of What If Season 2 as we compare it to the near-flawless season one. You don't have to listen to this episode multiple times but then again...What If?**Get 1 month FREE of Magic Mind, when you’re subscribing for 3 months at:** [**https://www.magicmind.com/JANmajorissues**](https://www.magicmind.com/JANmajorissues)**with my code: MAJORISSUES20 It’s an extra 20% off! This only lasts until the end of January, so hurry up before it goes away.**

